om/2018/09/18/Hexo使用技巧/","excerpt":"","text":"Hexo常用命令","categories":[],"tags":[],"keywords":[]},{"title":"Laravel-Admin Grid里面获取Filter的数据","slug":"Laravel-Admin-Grid里面获取Filter的数据表","date":"2018-09-18T10:22:14.000Z","updated":"2018-09-18T10:22:29.000Z","comments":true,"path":"2018/09/18/Laravel-Admin-Grid里面获取Filter的数据表/","link":"","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/2018/09/18/Laravel-Admin-Grid里面获取Filter的数据表/","excerpt":"","text":"&emsp;&emsp;在使用laravel-admin的过程中，总有些项目需要统计用户，订单，流水等数据，除了专门做个数据统计模块(结合chartjs等)，我们还可以选择在Grid页面直接显示统计数据。&emsp;&emsp;方案1：参照exporter的源码后，发现在Grid里面可以用：$grid-&gt;getFilter()-&gt;execute()获取到筛选出来的数据，但是下面的正常渲染会报错：BadMethodCallException In Macroable.php line 96 :Method hasGetMutator does not exist。疑似execute只能调用一次，有待进一步研究。&emsp;&emsp;方案2：覆盖laravel-admin默认视图，修改resources/views/admin/grid/table.blade.php，添加如下示例代码即可：12345678910111213&lt;!-- 自定义区 --&gt; @if(\\Illuminate\\Support\\Str::contains(\\Illuminate\\Support\\Facades\\Route::current()-&gt;uri,[&apos;admin/channel-manage/order&apos;,&apos;admin/order&apos;])) @php $totalBuy = 0; $totalWin = 0; foreach ($grid-&gt;rows() as $row)&#123; $totalBuy += $row-&gt;column(&apos;buy_price&apos;); $totalWin += $row-&gt;column(&apos;winning_total_price&apos;); &#125; @endphp 总消费额：&#123;&#123; $totalBuy &#125;&#125;元 &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; 总奖金：&#123;&#123; $totalWin &#125;&#125;元 @endif","categories":[],"tags":[],"keywords":[]},{"title":"Redis SubPub上下文的问题","slug":"Redis-SubPub上下文的问题","date":"2018-08-13T03:10:00.000Z","updated":"2018-08-13T03:22:27.000Z","comments":true,"path":"2018/08/13/Redis-SubPub上下文的问题/","link":"","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/2018/08/13/Redis-SubPub上下文的问题/","excerpt":"","text":"众所周知，Redis的发布订阅模式可以用来做实时队列。 很多时候我们的业务逻辑，很可能会在订阅的上下文（）中去操作Redis的数据，像get,set,publish之类的，但是Redis默认是不支持在subscribe的上下文执行除了取消订阅等少有的几个命令之外的其他命令的，解决办法就是：在sucscribe上下文中新建一个Redis连接实例，这样就可以用新的连接去执行任何Redis命令了。 伪代码：123456$redis1 = new Redis();$redis1-&gt;subscribe([&apos;channel&apos;],function($msg)&#123; $redis = new Redis(); $redis-&gt;get(&apos;key&apos;); ......&#125;); 注意不要用静态方法实例化，因为那样本质上还是使用的同一个连接。","categories":[],"tags":[],"keywords":[]},{"title":"PHP查看安装基本信息","slug":"PHP查看安装基本信息","date":"2018-08-04T08:36:41.000Z","updated":"2018-08-13T03:28:25.000Z","comments":true,"path":"2018/08/04/PHP查看安装基本信息/","link":"","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/2018/08/04/PHP查看安装基本信息/","excerpt":"","text":"新安装的PHP环境，如何查看安装详情12&lt;?php phpinfo();","categories":[{"name":"PHP","slug":"PHP","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/categories/PHP/"}],"tags":[{"name":"PHP","slug":"PHP","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/tags/PHP/"}],"keywords":[{"name":"PHP","slug":"PHP","permalink":"http://yoursite.com/categories/PHP/"}]}]}